              "settings": {
                "editor": "<img width=\"640\" height=\"398\" src=\"http://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Floor-Care-in-Washington-DC-e1705210969131-1024x636.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Floor-Care-in-Washington-DC-e1705210969131-1024x636.png 1024w, https://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Floor-Care-in-Washington-DC-e1705210969131-300x186.png 300w, https://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Floor-Care-in-Washington-DC-e1705210969131-768x477.png 768w, https://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Floor-Care-in-Washington-DC-e1705210969131-1536x954.png 1536w, https://midlandfloors.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Floor-Care-in-Washington-DC-e1705210969131.png 1952w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t 15\n\t\t\t\t    \t\t+\t\t\t\t    \t\n\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t\t\t    \t\tYears of Experience\t\n\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t 774\n\t\t\t\t    \t\t+\t\t\t\t    \t\n\t\t\t\t    \t\t\t\t\t    \t\tClients\t\n\t            Schedule a Visit <h2>Get an Instant Quote and Schedule A Site Visit\n</h2>\t\t\t\t\n            \t\t            \t\t<p>Discover our range of floor care packages, tailored for spaces of all sizes. Choose from Standard, Premium, or Custom options to meet your specific cleaning needs.</p><p>\u00a0</p><p>Get an instant quote today and schedule a site visit to ensure your floors always look their best.</p>  \n\t\t<p><strong>Choose from our range of floor care packages, designed to meet your specific needs with the convenience of recurring services.</strong></p><p><strong>Standard Package:</strong></p><ul><li>Service Frequency: Quarterly</li><li>Coverage: Carpet, Tile &amp; Grout, LVT</li><li>Area: Up to 5,000 sq ft</li></ul><p><strong>Premium Package:</strong></p><ul><li>Service Frequency: Quarterly</li><li>Coverage: Carpet, Tile &amp; Grout, LVT</li><li>Area: Up to 12,000 sq ft</li></ul><p><strong>Custom Package:</strong></p><ul><li>Fully customizable service frequency, flooring type, and \"Appearance Boosters\".</li><li>Ideal for one-time services or specific requirements.</li><li>Appearance Boosters include add-ons like high gloss floor finish or deodorizer for enhanced results.</li></ul><p><strong>Note:</strong> All packages are recurring services. One-time services fall under the Custom package.</p><p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/floor-care-services/\">Services</a></p><p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/about/\">About Midland</a></p><p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/\">Home</a></p><p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/faq/\">Frequently Asked Questions</a></p><p><a href=\"https://midlandfloors.com/ultimate-guide-to-floor-care-for-retail/\">Ultimate Guide to Floor Care for Retail</a></p><div style=\"background:#F3FCF4;border-left:4px solid #43A94B;padding:18px 22px;margin-top:24px;border-radius:6px\"><p style=\"margin:0 0 10px;font-size:13px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#0F1411\">Related Services</p><ul style=\"margin:0;padding-left:18px;line-height:1.9\"><li><a href=\"/long-term-recurring-commercial-floor-care-programs/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Long-Term & Recurring Commercial Floor Care Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/customized-commercial-floor-care-solutions/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Customized Commercial Floor Care Solutions</a></li><li><a href=\"/janitorial-housekeeping-facility-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Janitorial & Housekeeping Facility Services</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-upholstery/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Upholstery</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-tile-grout-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Tile & Grout Cleaning</a></li><li><a href=\"/commercial-carpet-cleaning-services/\" style=\"color:#2F8137;font-weight:700\">Commercial Carpet Cleaning Services</a></li></ul></div>",
